22 failures yielding a failure list longer than bugzilla will take as a comment.

their declaration/definitions encodings for search string creation updated

2) All failed tests use search to look for functions/method; the pattern
matching fails since it doesn't properly decode the return type which is now in
the index. Vlad has a patch that we put together to decode return strings -
putting this in will restore the ui tests.
